<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{subject}}</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset & Base Styles */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
            -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 6px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #000;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header img {
            height: 50px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        /* Enhanced Content Styles */
        .content {
            padding: 30px 40px;
        }
        .alert-box {
            background-color: #d03030;
            border-left: 4px solid #d32f2f;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .details-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 25px 0;
            background: #fafafa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .details-table tr:not(:last-child) {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .details-table td {
            padding: 12px 15px;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        .details-table td:first-child {
            font-weight: 600;
            width: 160px;
            color: #555;
            background: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .action-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #d32f2f;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .action-button:hover {
            background-color: #b71c1c;
        }
        
        /* Responsive Adjustments */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container { margin: 0; border-radius: 0; }
            .content { padding: 20px; }
            .details-table td { display: block; width: 100%; }
            .details-table td:first-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="./assets/apicts-logo.jpg" alt="{{companyName}} Logo">
            <h1>Login Attempt Notification</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
           <p>Hello <%= userName %>,</p>

            <div class="alert-box">
                <p>A login attempt was detected on your account from a new device. If this wasn't you, please contact support.</p>
            </div>

            <table class="details-table">
                <tr>
                    <td>Device:</td>
                    <td><%= deviceInfo %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Browser:</td>
                    <td><%= browserInfo %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>IP Address:</td>
                    <td><%= ipAddress %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Location:</td>
                    <td><%= location %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Time:</td>
                    <td><%= timestamp %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <p>If this was you, you can safely ignore this email. Otherwise, we recommend:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Changing your password immediately</li>
                <li>Enabling two-factor authentication</li>
                <li>Reviewing your recent account activity</li>
            </ul>
              <div style="display: flex;">
            Need help? <div style=" margin: 25px 0;">
                <a href="<%= contact %>" class="action-button">
                    Contact Support
                </a>
            </div>


           
            
        </div>
 <div>
                <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
                    Best regards,<br>
                    <strong>The Apicts Team</strong>
                </p>
            </div>
             
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> APICTS. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This is an automated notification. Please Do Not Reply To This Email.</p>
        </div>
       
    </div>
</body>
</html>
